title: The Plant Organic Cafe and Market
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Organic, Western, Juice bar, Take-out
description: Opened winter 2013, cafe always has raw cakes on display and all food is vegan. Drinks include juices, smoothies and coffee. Cafe opens at 11am. Store sells mainly vegan products, including organic produce, but does carry organic dairy products. Store opens at 9am.
